cs.LG, cs.IT, cs.NI, cs.SY, cs.DC 

The paper proposes a new algorithm for network-distributed optimization, which is a common problem in machine learning and optimization. The paper focuses on communication efficiency, which is a key concern in distributed optimization. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.IT (Information Theory) and cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture). The paper also deals with control systems (cs.SY) and distributed computing (cs.DC), which are relevant sub-categories.
